node.text:
We watched “fatherhood” and was crazy good movie hit home Bc I was raised by single father too S.O pops @kevinnishi wouldn’t be here without u. 

Korean corndogs
1 ¼ cup flour
½ ts salt & sugar
1 tb baking powder
1 egg
¾ cup milk
Hotdogs
Mozzarella 
Panko breadcrumbs

Tteokbokki
6 cup hondashi 6 TB gochujang 
2 TB red pepper flakes & sugar
2 to soysauce
Scallions
Mozzarella cheese (shredded)
Rice cakes 2lbs 
(We made large batch half the recipe of using less)***

#koreancorndogs #tteokbokki #moviemonday #datenight #cookingvideo #koreanfood

node.text:
This the best easiest Kung pao chicken you will ever make no 🧢

Ingredients

Onion
Red bell pepper
garlic
Dry chilli flakes
Chilli whole dry
Chicken thighs
Soy sauce
Sesame oil
Sugar
5 spice
Corn starch
cashews

Instructions

PREP: Onion sliced, red/yellow pepper chopped, zucchini chopped, 1 TB minced garlic,
Crushed cashews

Debone the chicken thighs and cut up into whatever size pieces u want, its ur food, i kept skin on

Chicken marinade: 1 TB Sugar, 1 ts rice vinegar, 2 TB soy sauce, ½ ts sesame oil, pinch five spice 2 TB cornstarch

Now shallow fry the chicken in BATCHES if u want the best outcome, if time is shmoney then do it all at once like ya boy, 5-6 mins its quick, set side on paper towel lined plate

Empty oil leaving a little bit and add onion, garlic, and 1-2 TB chilli flakes and/or dry whole chillis sliced depending on how spicy u want urs

Then add the rest of prepped veg, add 2 TB soy, 1 TB sugar, 1 TB oyster sauce,

Once veg softened add the chicken back, 

Cashews (optional)

Serve @ a safe distance

#cookingvideo #howtocook #asianfood #kungpaochicken

node.text:
KBBQ at home

Multiple reasons why its better but ill just say 2
Way cheaper
Ez af

Lmk ur perfect bite, i got 
Seaweed > with choice meat > kimchi > rice > slight dip in the sauce with red pepper flake
I actually wanna know how u eat KBBQ 👇

All u need to know if how to marinate the beef and u can “grill” the food on any electric skillet and jus have fun with the fam KBBQ @ homeee

Bulgogi
brown sugar, honey, soy sauce, rice wine, sesame oil, ginger, garlic, black peoper

Spicy Pork belly
Red pepper paste, red pepper, soy sauce, sesame oil, pepper, garlic, ginger, 

Brisket
thin sliced beef

Short ribs
Soy sauce, brown sugar, rice wine vinegar, garlic, ginger, black pepper

I forgot to make the Ban Chan or the sides but basically u just black anything then toss with sesame oil, salt, & sesame seeds to taste

#koreanbbq #cooking #bdaydinner #howtocook #cookingvideo #nishcooks

Rays Koumandra soup (Tom Yum) 🍲 

This movie I fw it heavy the message behind it is some real shiiit 🎥 

Ingredients
Shrimp
Galangel
Lemongrass
Limes
Fish sauce
Nam prik pow
Cilantro
Thai chillies
Cilantro
Roma tomato
White onion
Oyster mushrooms
Shrimp paste

Instructions
Prep: peel shrimp keep shells & heads, crush & cut lemongrass, slice glangel
Boil the shrimp shells 10 mins then strain
Add shrimp heads
Galangel(or ginger)

Add mushrooms, 1lb peeled shrimp
& raya kounamdra ingredients
1 TB Shrimp paste from tail
¼ cup Bamboo shoot
4 Chilies
⅓ cup Palm sugar from heart
4tb Lemongrass

Serve up add some rice if you like 🍚 
Idk how this supposed to be eaten but flips add rice to soup so Issa mover

Mini Calzones 🍕 

Don’t sleep on cooking dates try this. But even if u single u should try these calzones so EZ 👩‍🍳 

Easy pizza dough
- 2 cups flour
- 3/4 cup water
- 1 pack instant yeast
- 1/2 TB salt & sugar
- 1TB olive oil

Knead 10 mins and rest for 30 

#calzone #dateidea #pizza #howtocook #howtomakecalzones #cookingvideo

node.text:
Fish & Chips 🐠 🥔 

Actually heat

Ingredients
Beer
Baking soda
Flour
Starch
White fish (cod)
Vodka

Instructions
Prep for fish batter
Batter:  flour, corn starch, salt, season garlic powder, paprika - beer until it is smoothie consistency 
Dredge: flour corn starch, salt, season garlic powder paprika

Now season fish with salt >> dredge >> batter >> fry few mins till golden brown and crispy

Fries could use frozen fries or homemade
Homemade - russet potatoes cut into fries
and we will double fry but only in one batch, for 4 mins fry it in oil (Ned heat) then go hi heat and fry till golden brown and crispy
Tar tar sauce
½ C Mayo
½ lemon juice
2 dill pickles diced
Splash hot sauce
salt & pepper

Serve 

#fishchips #beerbatter #fish

node.text:
Cajun Chicken & Shrimp 🐔🦐 

Pasta be the easiest to make, go try this frfr

Ingredients

Chicken Breast 
Shrimp 
Bell Peppers 
Onions 
Celery 
Alfredo Sauce 
Butter 
Cajun Seasoning
Salt 
Fettuccine Noodles

Instructions

Prep: Dice celery, onion, and bell peppers. Cut chicken into cubes and season with cajun seasoning and salt. Peel shrimp and season with cajun seasoning and salt. 

Cook: Pour some olive oil on the pan and wait until it’s hot enough. Add in chicken and take off pan once cooked. Add a Tbsp of butter and throw in the shrimp. Take out once cooked. 

Throw in veggies, season with salt, and add a slice of butter. Add Alfredo sauce, cajun seasoning, chicken, shrimp, and cooked noodles. 

#cookingvideo #howtocook #pasta #Cajun #chicken #shrimp

node.text:
Mango habanero Wings 🍗 

Do not let me catch u don’t be wasting that hard earned Shmoney

Ingredients

Party wings
Mango
Garlic
Paprika
Lime
Honey
Ginger

Instructions
Wings pat dry season salt pepper
Toss with 1TB corn starch per pound wings to help with crispiness
Preheat oven to 400 and bake on a WIRE baking sheet for 35 mins

While that bakes start the sauce:
Into blender x1 mango, 2 habanero peppers, 2 garlic cloves, 1TB ginger,  x1 lime juice > blend
Then place into small pot bring to simmer and add ⅓  cup honey
Bring down heat and if like consistency thats good if want thicker add in corn starch slurry to thicken it up 
After 35 mins in over with convection on (basically turns your oven into an air fryer) take out and slap the wings generously with the mango habanero sauce

Back into oven under broiler for few mins to get the sauce nice and sticky

serve w carrots celery ranch/blue cheese whatever brah

#cookingvideo #howtocook #wings #homemadewings #bakedwings #mangohabenero
